By Sadie Gennis, 
Jim Carrey 's ex-girlfriend Cathriona White has committed suicide, TMZ reports. 
According to the site, the Los Angeles Police Department responded to a call on Monday night and found White's body at a local residence. Pills were discovered next to White and it's believed she died from a drug overdose. 
The 28-year-old reportedly left a suicide note addressed to Carrey, which referenced their split on Sept. 24. 
Carrey and White first dated in 2012, but split after a few months. However, they got back together in May.
